FT  20 OCT 94 / UK Company News: Aminex
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Aminex, the Dublin-listed oil and gas exploration group, turned post-tax
losses of IPounds 124,860 into profits of IPounds 481,778 (Pounds 476,159)
for the half-year to June 30.
Oil and gas revenue was boosted from IPounds 55,764 to IPounds 3.88m,
largely by Amkomi, the company's joint venture in the Komi Republic of
Russia.
